=== 美洲 ===
*{{Flagicon|Bolivia|variant=1826}}[[玻利维亚|玻利维亚]]，为[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]和[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=iOMoAAAAYAAJ&q=resoluci%C3%B3n+del+congreso+23+febrero+1825&pg=PA6 | title=Colección oficial de leyes, decretos, ordenes, resoluciones &c. Que se han expedido para el regimen de la Republica Boliviana| year=1826| author1=Bolivia}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon|Uruguay}}[[乌拉圭|乌拉圭]]在美洲殖民地独立运动初期为[[巴西帝国|巴西帝国]]和[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{cite web|title=Uruguay - From Insurrection to State Organization, 1820-30|url=http://countrystudies.us/uruguay/4.htm|website=countrystudies.us|access-date=3 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Phelps|first1=Nicole|title=Review of Knarr, James C., Uruguay and the United States, 1903-1929: Diplomacy in the Progressive Era|url=http://www.h-net.org/reviews/showrev.php?id=37009|website=www.h-net.org|access-date=3 March 2017|language=en|date=1 January 2014}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon|Paraguay|variant=1842}}[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]在[[巴拉圭战争|巴拉圭战争]]后作为[[巴西|巴西]]和阿根廷之间的缓冲国得以保留。<ref>{{cite news|title=Paraguay: Regional Geopolitics and a New President|url=https://www.stratfor.com/analysis/paraguay-regional-geopolitics-and-new-president|access-date=3 March 2017|work=Stratfor|language=en}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon image|Colonial-Red-Ensign.svg}}[[乔治亚省|乔治亚省]]是[[英国|英国]]于1732年创立的殖民地，为英属北美殖民地和[[西属佛罗里达|西属佛罗里达]]之间的缓冲。<ref>{{Cite web|title = The Colonies {{!}} Georgia|url = http://www.smplanet.com/teaching/colonialamerica/colonies/georgia|website = www.smplanet.com|access-date = 20 November 2015}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon|Ecuador}}[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]为秘鲁和[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vVYGkG1b9qgC&q=ecuador+estado+colchon+colombia+peru&pg=PA17|title = Ecuador: Relaciones exteriores a la luz del bicentenario|isbn = 9789978672242|last1 = Zepeda|first1 = Beatriz|year = 2009}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon|Canada}}[[加拿大|加拿大]]为[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]和[[美国|美国]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sukhankin |first1=Sergey |title=Russia and the Arctic in an Era of Strategic Competition |journal=North American and Arctic Defence and Security Network (NAADSN) |date=2021 |pages=19-49 |url=https://www.naadsn.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Sukhankin-Russia-Arctic.pdf |access-date=8 December 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Nuclear Power at Heart of Russia's Arctic Ambition |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-11381773 |access-date=8 December 2021 |publisher=BBC News |date=22 September 2010}}</ref>
=== 亚洲 ===
*在[[罗马－波斯战争|罗马－波斯战争]]期间，很多国家都起到了缓冲的作用。{{Flagicon image|Artaxiad coat of arms by PeopleOfAr.svg}}[[亚美尼亚王国|亚美尼亚王国]]就是[[波斯帝国|波斯帝国]]和[[罗马帝国|罗马帝国]]之间的缓冲国。
*{{Flagicon|North Korea}}[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]在[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]以后一直被视为[[中国|中国]]与[[韩国|韩国]]、[[日本|日本]]以及[[美国|美国]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Getting China to Become Tough with North Korea|url = http://www.cato.org/blog/getting-china-become-tough-north-korea|website = [[Cato_Institute|Cato Institute]]|access-date = 2016-02-10}}</ref>
*{{Flagicon|Manchukuo}}[[满洲国|满洲国]]为日本所扶植的[[傀儡政权|傀儡政权]]，在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间为[[苏联|苏联]]、[[中华民国|中华民国]]以及[[日本|日本]]之间的缓冲国，于二战后覆灭。
*{{Flagicon|Thailand}}[[泰国|泰国]]长期以来都是独立国家，充当[[英属印度|英属印度]]、[[英属马来亚|英属马来亚]]以及[[法属印度支那|法属印度支那]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{Cite book|title = LAOS, From Buffer State to Crossroads|last = Pholsena|first = Vatthana|publisher = Silkworm Books|year = 2007|isbn = 978-9749480502}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title = Through the Buffer State : Travels in Borneo, Siam, Cambodia, Malaya and Burma|last = Macgregor|first = John|publisher = White Lotus Co Ltd; 2 edition|year = 1994|isbn = 978-9748496252}}</ref>
*{{Flag|Korean Empire}}为[[日本帝国|日本帝国]]和[[俄罗斯帝国|俄罗斯帝国]]之间的缓冲国。
*{{Flag|Far Eastern Republic}}为日本帝国与俄罗斯帝国之间的缓冲国。<ref name="Wood">Alan Wood, "The Revolution and Civil War in Siberia," in Edward Acton, Vladimir Iu. Cherniaev, and William G. Rosenberg (eds.), ''Critical Companion to the Russian Revolution, 1914–1921''. Bloomington, IN: Indiana University Press, 1997; pp. 716–717.</ref><ref name="Dict">George Jackson and Robert Devlin (eds.), ''Dictionary of the Russian Revolution''. Westport, CT: Greenwood Press, 1989; pp. 223–225.</ref>
*{{Flag|Emirate of Afghanistan}}在[[大博弈|大博弈]]期间属于[[俄罗斯帝国|俄罗斯帝国]]和英国之间的缓冲国，当时[[南亚|南亚]]为大英帝国的势力范围，[[中亚|中亚]]为俄罗斯帝国的实力范围。随后，[[瓦罕走廊|瓦罕走廊]]将缓冲区延伸到了中国边境。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MtUpCwAAQBAJ|title=The Mountain: A Political History from the Enlightenment to the Present|last1=Debarbieux|first1=Bernard|last2=Rudaz|first2=Gilles|last3=Todd|first3=Jane Marie|last4=Price|first4=Martin F.|date=2015-09-10|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=9780226031118|page=150|language=en}}</ref>
*喜马拉雅山国家{{Flag|Kingdom of Nepal}}、{{Flag|Bhutan}}和{{Flag|Sikkim}}曾为中国和大英帝国之间的缓冲国，在1962年中印战争之后这三国成为了中国和印度之间的缓冲国，锡金随后被印度吞并。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Nepal: Dictated by Geography {{!}} World Policy Institute|url = http://www.worldpolicy.org/journal/winter2013/nepal-dictated-by-geography|website = www.worldpolicy.org|access-date = 2016-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title = The World Today; Bhutan and Sikkim: Two Buffer States Vol. 15, No. 12|publisher = Royal Institute of International Affairs|year = 1959|pages = 492–500}}</ref>
*{{Flag|Mongolia}}曾为中苏之间的缓冲国，苏联解体后成为了中俄之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mongolia, the uncontested buffer state|url=http://www.russia-direct.org/opinion/mongolia-uncontested-buffer-state|website=Russia Direct|access-date=3 March 2017|language=en|archive-date=4 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204190410/https://www.russia-direct.org/opinion/mongolia-uncontested-buffer-state|url-status=dead}}</ref>
*{{Flag|Lebanon}}为叙利亚和[[以色列|以色列]]之间的[[缓冲国|缓冲国]]。
=== 非洲 ===
*{{Flagicon image|Flag of Morocco 1258 1659.svg}}[[萨阿德王朝|摩洛哥]]在16世纪时为[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]之间的缓冲国。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Cory|first1=Stephen|title=Reviving the Islamic Caliphate in Early Modern Morocco|date=2016|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781317063438|pages=36–37}}</ref>
=== 欧洲 ===
*{{Flagicon|United Netherlands}}[[荷兰联合王国|荷兰联合王国]]今属于[[荷兰|荷兰]]和[[比利时|比利时]]，于[[维也纳会议|维也纳会议]]后成立，曾经为[[普鲁士|普鲁士]]、[[法国|法国]]和[[英国|英国]]之间的缓冲国。该国总共存在了15年，直到[[比利时独立|比利时独立]]。
*[[莱茵兰|莱茵兰]]在战间期属于[[德国|德国]]和[[法国|法国]]之间的缓冲，法国曾尝试建立[[莱茵共和国|莱茵共和国]]，但未获国际承认。<ref>{{cite news|title=THE RUHR: Rhineland Republic?|url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,716441,00.html|access-date=12 March 2017|work=Time|date=27 August 1923}}</ref>

